<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
    <key>title</key>
    <string>Oback</string>
    <key>items</key>
    <array>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSGroupCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>Oback 设置</string>
            <key>footerText</key>
            <string>OPPO 风格边缘手势返回（roothide / iOS 16.4.1）</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSwitchCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>左边缘返回</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>leftEnabled</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <true/>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>从屏幕左边缘向内滑动，触发返回上一页。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSwitchCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>右边缘返回</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>rightEnabled</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <true/>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>从屏幕右边缘向内滑动返回，部分系统 App（如相机）可能不支持。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSwitchCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>触感反馈</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>hapticEnabled</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <true/>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>到达提交阈值时触发轻微震动，提供操作确认感。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSwitchCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>当前页阴影</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>shadowEnabled</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <true/>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>返回过程中给当前页面叠加投影，增强层叠立体感。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>触发宽度 (pt)</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>triggerWidth</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>24</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>8</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>60</real>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>屏幕边缘多宽的范围会被识别为返回手势（8–60 点）。越宽越容易误触，越窄越难触发。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>视差位移</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>parallaxOffset</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>0.3</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>0</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>0.6</real>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>上一页随手势探出的位移比例，数值越大探出越明显（0–0.6）。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>上一页最小缩放</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>previousScaleMin</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>0.92</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>0.8</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>1</real>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>静止时上一页的最小缩放比例，营造纵深效果（0.8–1.0）。调小纵深感更强。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>遮罩浓度</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>dimAlpha</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>0.35</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>0</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>0.8</real>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>返回时覆盖在上一页上的暗色遮罩强度（0–0.8）。越大越暗，对比越强烈。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSliderCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>动画时长 (s)</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>duration</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <real>0.32</real>
            <key>min</key>
            <real>0.15</real>
            <key>max</key>
            <real>0.6</real>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>松手后完成或取消返回动画的时长（0.15–0.6 秒）。越短越跟手，越长越顺滑。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSGroupCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>生效范围</string>
            <key>footerText</key>
            <string>开启「启用白名单」后，只有下方选中的 App 有手势返回，其余一律不生效（默认）。关闭则全局生效、下方黑名单内的 App 排除。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSSwitchCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>启用白名单</string>
            <key>key</key>
            <string>whitelistMode</string>
            <key>defaults</key>
            <string>com.zlhkf.oback</string>
            <key>default</key>
            <true/>
            <key>footnote</key>
            <string>开：仅「选白名单程序」中的 App 生效。关：所有 App 生效，并排除「选黑名单程序」中的 App。</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSLinkCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>选白名单程序</string>
            <key>detail</key>
            <string>ObackWhiteListController</string>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>cell</key>
            <string>PSLinkCell</string>
            <key>label</key>
            <string>选黑名单程序</string>
            <key>detail</key>
            <string>ObackBlackListController</string>
        </dict>
    </array>
</dict>
</plist>
